text.__SUMMARY__: Shorea hypoleuca is a species of plant in the Dipterocarpaceae family. It is endemic to Borneo.
text.Sources: Ashton, P. (1998). "Shorea hypoleuca". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33415A9781872. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33415A9781872.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
